content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1262.40 - Transfer of bulk fuel within terminal boundaries prohibited

State Regulations

The transfer of bulk aircraft or commercial fuel from
one fuel service vehicle to another is prohibited within the boundaries of an
air terminal without permission. Notes
